<HL>
   Who's News:
   Bowler Quits as Porsche U.S. Unit's Chief,
   Cites Dispute Over Goals; Schwab Gets Job
   ----
   By Jacqueline Mitchell
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
03/09/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<CO>
   G.POR WNEWS
</CO>
